title: Voices of Ascension - Ava Maria 320cbr 1993 Christmas Music
description:
Source: 1993 CD
 
Voices of Ascension - Ava Maria 320cbr (Big Papi) 1993 Christmas Music 

 
Not sure who these folks are but they are not weekend warriors who happened to join a choir.  They are skilled asrtists.  This is simply amazing church type choir music that seems to blend choir and chant in some songs, cobnjuring up how songs would sound like 1,500 years ago. Very soothing, spiritual and relaxing.  I have it listed as Christmas music since Ava Maria is in there but it appears this music is for all seasons. - Big Papi
